测。最终车主同意放弃向保险索赔自行承担本次事故全部损失费用，现场与保险公司签订《放弃赔偿声明》并记录留档。 小米汽车称，2月6日，门店和工程团队去往事故现场实地考察，再结合车辆受损部位的痕迹，推断用户车辆在该路况下严重超速行驶，同时车辆受到路坑边缘冲击，轮胎异常受力后爆胎，而后冲击力直接传递到轮圈、摆臂上，导致摆臂受力过载后断裂，并非个别谣传断轴。最终，车辆右后悬架损坏，空气弹簧滑出，车辆继续滑行，摆臂以及减振器等受到磨损。车辆检测结果为事故的外力受损，非产品质量问题。 小米回应“SU7被曝过坑时发生断轴”：不实，超速驾驶导致事故_澎湃质量观_澎湃新闻-The Paper"},"attached_info":"CkIIx8SI1rnz26ReEAMaCTExMzMxNjUzNiDWrKC9BjAAOPcFQAVyCzExNzA0MTEyMzMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"103 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f9e1484ed64b667bfbfa0f28c8071a9a_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1739151241.249201","card_id":"Q_354758934","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":354758934,"title":"怎么现在的年轻人都不愿意和老人住在一起？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/354758934","type":"question","created":1573171008,"answer_count":32,"follower_count":83,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5583,152296,165936],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4Ix8SI1rnz26ReEAMaCDQxMTEzMjA0IMDeku4FMAA4U0AGcgkzNTQ3NTg5MzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"80 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-2eb2133cd56fc27645fb7734dc2f8968_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1739151241.249564","card_id":"Q_10847928427","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":10847928427,"title":"《哪吒之魔童闹海》中敖光向敖丙道歉，长辈应不应该用自己的经验去规训引导孩子？还是尊重孩子的独立选择？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/10847928427","type"